  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELCOME TO MAYHEM! </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/76187c73a689fba79a3fd38835308322.poster.avif?t=1673287967\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/76187c73a689fba79a3fd38835308322.webm?t=1673287967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/76187c73a689fba79a3fd38835308322.mp4?t=1673287967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Try our signature mode that cycles through 3 phases: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Buy Phase:</strong> Earn Benjamins by slaughtering your enemies (and probably friends) to upgrade your equipment and gain abilities to compliment your play style.<br></li><li><strong>Event Phase:</strong> Participate in various game modes such as Zombie Invasion, Team Deathmatch, King of the Hill, and more!<br></li><li><strong>Free-For-All:</strong> Coming out of the event phase it's every stick for themselves! You may be forced to turn on your old teammates to get the dub!  </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SLAM ENERGY DRINKS!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/36e8c92f309b88ad8f1b71bb7d87edad.poster.avif?t=1673287967\" width=614 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/36e8c92f309b88ad8f1b71bb7d87edad.webm?t=1673287967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/36e8c92f309b88ad8f1b71bb7d87edad.mp4?t=1673287967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use energy to turn your weapons up a notch, unlocking powerful special abilities unique to each weapon! Use weapons together to create insane combos to obliterate your enemies!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WELCOME TO MAYHEM! </h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/76187c73a689fba79a3fd38835308322.poster.avif?t=1673287967\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/76187c73a689fba79a3fd38835308322.webm?t=1673287967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/76187c73a689fba79a3fd38835308322.mp4?t=1673287967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Try our signature mode that cycles through 3 phases: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Buy Phase:</strong> Earn Benjamins by slaughtering your enemies (and probably friends) to upgrade your equipment and gain abilities to compliment your play style.<br></li><li><strong>Event Phase:</strong> Participate in various game modes such as Zombie Invasion, Team Deathmatch, King of the Hill, and more!<br></li><li><strong>Free-For-All:</strong> Coming out of the event phase it's every stick for themselves! You may be forced to turn on your old teammates to get the dub!  </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SLAM ENERGY DRINKS!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/36e8c92f309b88ad8f1b71bb7d87edad.poster.avif?t=1673287967\" width=614 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/36e8c92f309b88ad8f1b71bb7d87edad.webm?t=1673287967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777120/extras/36e8c92f309b88ad8f1b71bb7d87edad.mp4?t=1673287967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use energy to turn your weapons up a notch, unlocking 